Question:https://leetcode.com/problems/maximum-number-of-operations-to-move-ones-to-the-end/

Solution:
class Solution {
    public int maxOperations(String s) {
        
        int operation=0,ones=0;
        boolean found = false;

        for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++) {
            if(s.charAt(i)=='1') {
                found = true;
                ones++;
            }

            if(found && s.charAt(i)=='0') {
                operation+=ones;
                found = false;
            }
        }

        return operation;
    }
}

/*
    s = "1001101" 
    i=0 -> 0001111


 */
